00:00:16.460 --> 00:00:18.960
So, here we are with Dj Noppe

00:00:18.960 --> 00:00:25.220
in the backroom of Berlin´s „Asphalt Club", right next to Gendarmenmarkt right in the centre

00:00:25.220 --> 00:00:26.529
of the capital.

00:00:26.529 --> 00:00:30.469
So first I really would like to know, when you first started using the name?

00:00:30.469 --> 00:00:34.040
The first time I was seventeen or eighteen years old and

00:00:34.040 --> 00:00:36.960
I saw, how the Dj mixed with the records

00:00:36.960 --> 00:00:38.330
and that was

00:00:38.330 --> 00:00:39.420
my biggest

00:00:39.420 --> 00:00:42.140
inspiration

00:00:42.140 --> 00:00:43.140
and i've tried it

00:00:43.140 --> 00:00:46.230
I tried it. I learned and learned, all day, all night,

00:00:46.230 --> 00:00:47.640
all night long.

00:00:47.640 --> 00:00:50.860
I learned and learned and yeah,

00:00:52.180 --> 00:00:55.710
this was the first step. Then they asked me, hey, which name

00:00:55.710 --> 00:00:58.740
we have to put on the flyer

00:00:58.740 --> 00:00:59.840
mhm, and I said: Dj Noppe.

00:00:59.840 --> 00:01:02.630
