00:01:02.630 --> 00:01:03.760
okay

00:01:03.760 --> 00:01:10.760
Take the same thing of the mixed tape!

00:01:20.720 --> 00:01:22.680
I know a lot of Djs, they stopped Dj`ing,

00:01:22.680 --> 00:01:27.880
because they don´t like the new sound no more and

00:01:27.880 --> 00:01:28.819
but

00:01:28.819 --> 00:01:32.440
for me I need the new sound every time

00:01:32.440 --> 00:01:36.640
I mix it up with old classics,

00:01:36.640 --> 00:01:38.760
some favourite songs, but

00:01:38.760 --> 00:01:41.220
basically I need

00:01:41.220 --> 00:01:43.740
the new songs

00:01:43.740 --> 00:01:50.740
and ehm...it´s fine...

00:02:12.109 --> 00:02:14.419
